summary:
The engineer with twenty-year experience in various branches of production (instrument making, power, shipbuilding, machine-tool construction) looks for distant work of the technical writer. The translation of instructions, representations, advertizing production into Russian, with the further lexical and technical processing according to standards meeting the requirements to registration of the text.
  Work on interaction and technical support with Russian-speaking users on trading floors and the sites is possible. Participation in exhibitions and seminars with Russian-speaking partners. Blogging on social networks and on the youtube.com channel with reviews of your production.
